 <purpose>
   <p>
     This part of ISO 10303 specifies an application module for the
     representation of the information needed to describe curve fonts used in CAD systems.
	   Included is information related to style, appearance and a predefined curve font.
	   Exchange of externally defined curve font is supported.
   </p>
 </purpose>

